altername_name: 인터랙티브 멀티 게임 체험판 디스크: 버전 29
name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 29
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v29 is a demo and video sampler disc, designed for retail store displays of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of Chicken Little, The Incredible Hulk: Ultimate Destruction, Donkey Konga 2, and Mario Superstar Baseball. The disc also features videos of the following: The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess, Battalion Wars, Mario Superstar Baseball, Medal of Honor: European Assault, The Incredible Hulk: Ultimate Destruction, Chicken Little, Charlie and the Chocolate Factory, Madden NFL 06, Fantastic 4, WWE Day of Reckoning 2, the Nintendo DS, and an ESRB ratings video.
